[Врожденный и Приобретенный Иммунитет](/%d1%82%d0%b5%d0%bb%d0%be-%d1%87%d0%b5%d0%bb%d0%be%d0%b2%d0%b5%d0%ba%d0%b0/%d0%be%d1%80%d0%b3%d0%b0%d0%bd%d0%b8%d0%b7%d0%bc/%d1%81%d0%b8%d1%81%d1%82%d0%b5%d0%bc%d0%b0-%d0%be%d1%80%d0%b3%d0%b0%d0%bd%d0%be%d0%b2/%d0%b8%d0%bc%d0%bc%d1%83%d0%bd%d0%bd%d0%b0%d1%8f-%d1%81%d0%b8%d1%81%d1%82%d0%b5%d0%bc%d0%b0/%d0%b2%d1%80%d0%be%d0%b6%d0%b4%d0%b5%d0%bd%d0%bd%d1%8b%d0%b9-%d0%b8-%d0%bf%d1%80%d0%b8%d0%be%d0%b1%d1%80%d0%b5%d1%82%d0%b5%d0%bd%d0%bd%d1%8b%d0%b9-%d0%b8%d0%bc%d0%bc%d1%83%d0%bd%d0%b8%d1%82%d0%b5/)

Макрофаги

[В -клетки](/%d1%82%d0%b5%d0%bb%d0%be-%d1%87%d0%b5%d0%bb%d0%be%d0%b2%d0%b5%d0%ba%d0%b0/%d0%be%d1%80%d0%b3%d0%b0%d0%bd%d0%b8%d0%b7%d0%bc/%d0%ba%d0%bb%d0%b5%d1%82%d0%ba%d0%b0/%d0%bb%d0%b8%d0%bc%d1%84%d0%be%d1%86%d0%b8%d1%82%d1%8b/%d0%b2-%d0%bb%d0%b8%d0%bc%d1%84%d0%be%d1%86%d0%b8%d1%82%d1%8b/)

[К-клетки](/%d1%82%d0%b5%d0%bb%d0%be-%d1%87%d0%b5%d0%bb%d0%be%d0%b2%d0%b5%d0%ba%d0%b0/%d0%be%d1%80%d0%b3%d0%b0%d0%bd%d0%b8%d0%b7%d0%bc/%d0%ba%d0%bb%d0%b5%d1%82%d0%ba%d0%b0/%d0%bb%d0%b8%d0%bc%d1%84%d0%be%d1%86%d0%b8%d1%82%d1%8b/%d0%ba-%d0%ba%d0%bb%d0%b5%d1%82%d0%ba%d0%b8/)

[Т-клетки](/%d1%82%d0%b5%d0%bb%d0%be-%d1%87%d0%b5%d0%bb%d0%be%d0%b2%d0%b5%d0%ba%d0%b0/%d0%be%d1%80%d0%b3%d0%b0%d0%bd%d0%b8%d0%b7%d0%bc/%d0%ba%d0%bb%d0%b5%d1%82%d0%ba%d0%b0/%d0%bb%d0%b8%d0%bc%d1%84%d0%be%d1%86%d0%b8%d1%82%d1%8b/%d0%ba-%d0%ba%d0%bb%d0%b5%d1%82%d0%ba%d0%b8/)

